  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nIt would be useful to add a flag that allows attach the built OpenAPI schema files (yaml/JSON) as build artifacts.\r\n\r\nThis feature is available in the `smallrye-open-api` (https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-open-api/tree/main/tools/maven-plugin#configuration-options) `attachArtifacts (boolean, default: false) - Attach the built OpenAPI schema as build artifact` and the configuration property could be mapped as `quarkus.smallrye-openapi.attach-artifacts`.\r\n\r\nThanks.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
